('160e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440015', '130e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440005', NULL, 'Task 1', 'Write a 150-word report describing the chart. The chart shows the percentage of renewable energy sources used in different countries in 2020. Germany had the highest percentage at 45%, followed by Denmark at 40%, and the United Kingdom at 35%. Japan had the lowest percentage at 15%. The chart illustrates the varying levels of renewable energy adoption across different nations, with European countries generally showing higher percentages compared to Asian countries.', '/test/image.jpg', 'essay', 1, '1', 1),
('160e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440016', '130e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440005', NULL, 'Task 2', 'Write a 250-word essay on the given topic. Some people believe that technology has improved our lives significantly, while others argue that it has created more problems than it has solved. Discuss both views and give your own opinion. Technology has undoubtedly transformed modern society in numerous ways. On one hand, it has revolutionized communication, healthcare, and education, making information more accessible and improving quality of life. On the other hand, concerns about privacy, job displacement, and social isolation have emerged. It is essential to consider both perspectives when evaluating technology''s impact on our lives.', NULL, 'essay', 2, '2', 1),
('160e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440017', '130e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440029', NULL, 'Task 1', 'Write a 150-word description of the chart provided. The bar chart illustrates the percentage of renewable energy sources used in different countries in 2020. Overall, Germany had the highest percentage at 45%, followed by Denmark at 40%, and the United Kingdom at 35%. Japan had the lowest percentage at 15%. The chart demonstrates the varying levels of renewable energy adoption across different nations, with European countries generally showing higher percentages compared to Asian countries.', '/test/image.jpg', 'essay', 1, '1', 1),
('160e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440018', '130e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440030', NULL, 'Task 2', 'Write a 250-word essay on the given topic. Many people believe that social media has had a negative impact on society, while others argue that it has brought people closer together. Discuss both views and give your own opinion. Social media platforms have become an integral part of modern life, connecting billions of people worldwide. Proponents argue that social media facilitates communication, enables information sharing, and helps maintain relationships across distances. Critics, however, point to issues such as cyberbullying, privacy concerns, and the spread of misinformation. The debate continues as we navigate the complex relationship between social media and society.', NULL, 'essay', 1, '1', 1),
('160e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440019', '130e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440035', NULL, 'Task 1', 'Write a letter for General Training. You recently stayed at a hotel and were not satisfied with the service. Write a letter to the hotel manager explaining what went wrong and what you would like them to do about it. Include details about your stay, the specific problems you encountered, and your expectations for resolution. The letter should be formal but polite, clearly stating your concerns and desired outcome.', NULL, 'essay', 1, '1', 1);

